1	Organizational Strategic Alignment	\N	Welcome to the Organizational Strategic Alignment assessment. 	The Organizational Strategic Alignment™ (OSA) assessment measures your organization's capability to execute its strategy. Specifically, it measures your organization’s deep drivers (similar to an individual’s DNA) which determine its culture and guides it performance.\n<br><br>\nThe results provide management and you with a snapshot of the underlying structure and dynamics of your organization.\n<br><br>\nThe questionnaire consists of 63 questions and 7 demographic questions. Most people complete the entire questionnaire in 10 minutes. Please answer the questions from your own perspective and experience. \n<br><br>\nAll individual results are kept completely anonymous and confidential and will never be shared on an individual basis.\n<br><br>\nThank you,\n<br><br>\nStrategia Analytics Team\n	Thank you for responding to this assessment.	We appreciate your responses and your insights. If you have any questions about the assessment, please contact Strategia Analytics at <a href="http://www.strategiaanalytics.com">www.strategiaanalytics.com</a>.\n<br><br>\nThe Strategia Analytics Team	0	\N	0	en
2	Executive Preference Profile	\N	Welcome to the Executive Preference Profile&trade; (EPP).	This brief assessment reveals the organizational culture in which you most comfortably work. The results provide you with the alignment of the behaviors, processes, and mindsets of the organization in which you work best.\n<br><br>\nPlease answer the questions from your <strong>own perspective and experience</strong> based on the organizations in which you <strong>most enjoyed working</strong>. The questionnaire takes 5-10 minutes to answer. There are <strong>no right or wrong answers</strong>, just your preferences.\n<br><br>\nThe Executive Preference Profile’s results examine the different approaches to building organizational culture preferences in executive teams.\n<br><br>\nThank you,\n<br><br>\nThe Strategia Analytics Team	Thank you for responding to this assessment.	We appreciate your responses and your insights. If you have any questions about the assessment, please contact Strategia Analytics at <a href="http://www.strategiaanalytics.com">www.strategiaanalytics.com</a>.\n<br><br>\nThe Strategia Analytics Team	0	\N	0	en
